# Hugging Face Spaces — Docker SDK.
#
# To use:
#   1. https://huggingface.co/new-space → SDK = "Docker", Hardware = CPU basic.
#   2. Push this repo (or set Spaces to mirror your GitHub repo).
#   3. In Settings → Variables and secrets, add:
#        - GOOGLE_API_KEY  (secret)
#        - PORT = 7860     (variable; HF Spaces standard port)
#        - APP_ENV = production
#        - ADK_MODEL = gemini-flash-latest
#   4. The Space rebuilds automatically; first boot auto-ingests the docs.
#
# No actual config schema — Spaces reads README.md frontmatter for SDK
# settings. This file is here as a pointer to the docs.
#
# Add the following frontmatter at the top of README.md when deploying
# to HF Spaces (we keep it out of the canonical README so the GitHub
# rendering stays clean):
#
# ---
# title: Helix SROP
# emoji: 🛰️
# colorFrom: blue
# colorTo: indigo
# sdk: docker
# app_port: 7860
# pinned: false
# ---
